							<div style='float:left; margin-right:20px;'><span style='color:#606060;'>Written by James Richardson</div>
							<div style='float:left; margin-right:20px;'><span style='color:#606060;'>Views:</span> <span name='page_views' id='page_views'>13,027</span></div>
